title.narrative: Second National Environmental Project - Phase II

description.narrative: The Project Development Objective is to contribute to strengthening environmental capacity in key Brazilian institutions. This would be accomplished by enhancing the environmental management capacity of institutions at the Federal, State, Federal District and Municipal levels and by demonstrating the effectiveness of targeted subprojects focused on defined priorities.
